item.title: First Toastmasters Yamanote event
item.description: 23:14 Friday 18 May 2018 JST Toastmasters Yamanote Club had its 360th event this evening, which was my first. The meeting was not in their normal location, but it included lots of mini-presentations and presentations about presentations and an overview presentation of the evening of presentations.
